title: Why cannot I open some pictures or video files on my phone?
answer:
l   File formats are not supported. 


 l   The memory of your phone is insufficient. 

 l   Files are damaged. 

 l   (DCF) files are under copyright protection. 

 l   The battery is low. 

 l   Unknown errors occurred in the phone's OS or applications. Restart the phone or reset it to factory defaults.****
